      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of April 15 travel item about wine-oriented tours in Tuscany (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A report in the April 15 In Transit column, about wine-oriented tours in Tuscany, misstated a popular dish there. It is pollo con peperoni (chicken with peppers), not pollo con pepperoni.</p>
      </block>
